==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''dicotyledon'''
# {{botany}} any plant in what used to be the ''[[Dicotyledones]]'' (also written ''Dicotyledonae''). Dicotyledons and [[monocotyledon]]s together make up the [[flowering plant]]s, the [[angiosperms]]. Examples of dicotyledons are [[bean]]s, [[buttercup]]s, [[oak]]s, [[sunflower]]s, etc.

